stories.title: Buttler braced to ramp up pressure on Australia
stories.subTitle: England v Australia, Group A, Edgbaston
stories.seoTitle: Jos Buttler braced to ramp up pressure on Australia
stories.summary: Jos Buttler admitted it would be "nice" to knock Australia out of the Champions Trophy when the sides meet at Edgbaston on Saturday.

stories.subTitle: Australia v England, Champions Trophy, Edgbaston

stories.title: Vaughan leads England to victory
stories.subTitle: Australia v England, Champions Trophy, Edgbaston
